Package: SGNB
Title: Splicing Graph-based Negative Binomial Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Yang", "Liu", email = "lylyf1987@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides an isoform-free model for detecting
    differentially expressed (DE) genes under two different conditions.
    In this analysis, a gene is defined as a non-DE gene if and only if 
    all its isoforms have the same expression level under two conditions.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
